chav1961.purelib.basic

Class ClassLoaderWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • chav1961.purelib.basic.ClassLoaderWrapper

  • public class ClassLoaderWrapper
extends ClassLoader

    This class is a wrapper to class loader for the current thread. It can create new class by it's definition (as byte array with class file content, so reader with the bytecode assembler inside AsmWriter.)

    The class is not thread-safe

    Since:
    0.0.2
    Author:
    Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
